snippet.textDisplay: As much as the previous years had some amazing games, 1994 is the first year I would personally call amazing in terms of gaming. The SNES was especially mind blowing and this is when it really separated itself from its competition. Quite a few of my favorite games of all time were released then: Donkey Kong Country (#29), Final Fantasy VI (#12), Super Metroid (#4) and Earthbound (#2). 1994 also gave us games that started popular franchises like Tekken, King of Fighters, Earthworm Jim, Warcraft, System Shock, etc. Still, I had to go with Earthbound here because as you all know by now, it has my favorite soundtrack ever. I'm due for another playthrough soon.
